<!-- WHY WE STARTED -->
<section style="padding: 100px 80px; max-width: 1300px; margin: 0 auto;">
  <div class="why-section" style="padding: 0; margin: 0;">
    <div class="why-visual">
      <div class="why-card-main" style="opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px);transition:opacity 0.7s,transform 0.7s" id="why-card">
        <blockquote>
          My mother wants to stay in her home. She wants to do her own shopping, get to her appointments, keep living her own life in her home. She just needs someone reliable by her side to make that possible.
        </blockquote>
        <div class="why-attribution">
          <div class="why-avatar">🌿</div>
          <div>
            <div class="why-attr-name">The moment that started it all</div>
            <div class="why-attr-title">Active Aging Partners · Atlanta, GA</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
      </div>
      <div class="why-card-float">
        <div class="why-float-icon">💡</div>
        <div class="why-float-text"><strong>The gap we found:</strong> Families need more than delivery apps and ride shares. They need a trusted person — someone who shows up, pays attention, and genuinely cares.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="why-text">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Why We Started</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">A personal story<br>that became <em>our purpose</em></h2>
      <p class="why-body">Active Aging Partners was born from a challenge our own family faces. Our mother lives out of state and is determined to remain independent — in her home, on her terms. But as time goes on, she needs more support: someone to walk with her, to take her to doctor's appointments and make sure she gets there safely, and to do her grocery shopping the <em>right</em> way — because grocery delivery services never get it quite right.</p>
      <p class="why-body">We searched for a service that could provide exactly that kind of personal, attentive care. We couldn't find one that truly fit. <strong>So we built it.</strong></p>
      <p class="why-body">Active Aging Partners is for every family navigating that same tension — the deep respect for a loved one's independence, and the very real need to know they are safe, active, and genuinely cared for. We bring the kind of attention and reliability that no app can replicate.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

